org.clafer.ast

Class AstClafer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.clafer.ast.AstClafer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AstVar
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AstAbstractClafer, AstConcreteClafer, AstPrimClafer

    public abstract class AstClafer
extends Object
implements AstVar
    A Clafer in the model. A Clafer represents both the set and the type. A concrete is either abstract, concrete, or primitive.
    Author:
    jimmy
